"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The Pentagon has confirmed that a US submarine sank an Iranian warship in the Indian Ocean. This incident has increased tensions between the US and Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Submarine Sinks Iranian Warship\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Pent\u00e1gono confirm\u00f3 que un submarino de EE.UU. hundi\u00f3 un barco de guerra iran\u00ed en el Oc\u00e9ano \u00cdndico. Este incidente ha aumentado las tensiones entre EE.UU. e Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Submarino de EE.UU. hunde barco iran\u00ed\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"US soldiers were killed after a drone evaded air defenses and hit a command center in Port Shuaiba, Kuwait. This attack highlights the ongoing conflict in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attack in Kuwait\",            \"translated_version\": \"Soldados de EE.UU. murieron despu\u00e9s de que un dron evit\u00f3 defensas a\u00e9reas y golpe\u00f3 un centro de mando en Puerto Shuaiba, Kuwait. Este ataque muestra el conflicto en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de dron en Kuwait\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The Arctic Metagaz, a ship, sank between Libya and Malta after it was hit by explosions and a fire. Libyan officials are investigating the cause of the incident.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ship Sinks Near Libya\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Arctic Metagaz, un barco, se hundi\u00f3 entre Libia y Malta despu\u00e9s de ser golpeado por explosiones y un incendio. Oficiales libios investigan la causa del incidente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Barco se hunde cerca de Libia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Spain's prime minister strongly responded to US President Donald Trump's threat to end trade with Spain. This disagreement could affect international relations.\",            \"english_title\": \"Spain Responds to US Threat\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de Espa\u00f1a respondi\u00f3 fuertemente a la amenaza del presidente de EE.UU., Donald Trump, de terminar el comercio con Espa\u00f1a. Este desacuerdo podr\u00eda afectar las relaciones internacionales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Espa\u00f1a responde a amenaza de EE.UU.\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Civilians are being displaced and are taking shelter in tents, parks, and cars as Israel retaliates to a Hezbollah rocket attack. The conflict is causing a humanitarian crisis.\",            \"english_title\": \"Civilians Displaced in Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Civiles est\u00e1n siendo desplazados y se refugian en tiendas, parques y coches mientras Israel responde a un ataque de cohetes de Hezbollah. El conflicto est\u00e1 causando una crisis humanitaria.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Civiles desplazados en conflicto\"        }    ]}"